{"id":603859,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/01/【立此存照】各级政府部门注意-警惕舆论阵地失守/","date":"2019-01-14T05:06:35Z","modified":"2019-01-14T05:12:53Z","title":"【立此存照】各级政府部门注意 警惕舆论阵地失守","content":"<p>近日，四川省乐山市沐川县有当地网友以“沐川老乡交流平台”的方式，组建微信群打通了当地195个行政村的联络，引起了当地政府的高度警惕，除了对牵头人士进行维稳外，要求对入群村民进行劝退，高呼“要高度重视网络意识形态工作，防止舆论监管真空地，守好舆论引导主阵地”。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-603861\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/DwpsuuXXQAIfbDU.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"557\" height=\"716\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/DwpsuuXXQAIfbDU.jpg 557w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/DwpsuuXXQAIfbDU-233x300.jpg 233w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 557px) 100vw, 557px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-603860\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/DwpsuuaXgAAOvsW.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"524\" height=\"355\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/DwpsuuaXgAAOvsW.jpg 524w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/DwpsuuaXgAAOvsW-300x203.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 524px) 100vw, 524px\" /></p>\n","author":1001,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[9526,37612,9432,21170,33267,9375,37611,37616,9503,37614,37615,37610,37613]}